---
title: Sheet Pan Curry Cauliflower Wraps with Potato Wedges & Curry Aïoli
description: There are so many reasons why we love a hearty wrap… but the main one? We get to enjoy our favorite veggies and sauces, all at the same time. This Indian-flavor-inspired, veggie-centric version stars cumin-and-paprika-spiced cauliflower, a curry cabbage slaw with golden raisins, and creamy curry aïoli. On the side, there’s more of the aïoli for dipping crispy potato wedges. Now that’s a dinner that’s sure to curry a lot of flavor.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/curry-cauliflower-cabbage-wraps-f7e557ea.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sheet-pan-curry-cauliflower-wraps-61264ec3f4a88439bd093d1f-cddc4c1f.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Indian
author: HelloFresh
